original_title: Queens: Old Bowery Bay Road - 88th Street
text:
Old Bowery Road (no longer in existence), east from 88th Street, showing from fore to background on the north side of the Road, the A. Klein and Conard Witte houses in 1909. On the opposite side of the Road is the Daniel Rapelje farmhouse, owned by S. Hirschman in 1909. All houses in this area no longer appear in 1926. If locating these houses in 1937 in the order above mentioned, they would be at the N.W. corner of 89th Street and Thirty-second Avenue, at the S.E. corner of 90th Street and Thirty-second Avenue; and at the S.E. corner of 89th Street and Thirty-second Avenue. This is a set of two views.

April 1924.
Views 1 and 2

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
